OHDEH
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 24th day of June, 2011, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal, treated as a Petition for Review, the Application for Stay, the Motion to Strike Default Judgment, and the Petition for Special Injunction are DENIED.
